item.title: CVE-2023-2493|2024-08-02T06:26:09.150Z -- unknown -- all%20in%20one%20redirection
item.description: The All In One Redirection WordPress plugin before 2.2.0 does not properly sanitise and escape multiple parameters before using them in an SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by high privilege users such as admin.
